6:
*sigh* I don't know what came over
me...
9:
You were very impressive. 
It was a one-of-a-kind experience.
13:
Besides, you got a ton of publicity
from it. Palpebra's practically
buzzing with your name.
17:
You say that like I should be happy
about it! Now everyone must think
I'm some kind of weirdo!
24:
We need to drum up even more
press. Take these and hand them
out!
28:
Are these... tissue packets? With the
little ads in the packaging?
31:
Impressive, right? They look exactly
like the ones back home.
32:
Took a lot of effort to get them
prepped, but I had a feeling we'd
need them in this Saga too!
34:
I have factories mass producing
them right now! Aren't I AMAZING!
AHAHAHA!
39:
Hey, these are actually a pretty
good idea. I always end up using
'em since they're so convenient.
44:
I'm an idol, not a part-timer that you
hired to do your job for you!
50:
Look closer, stupid head! These ads
are for the restaurant that's
sponsoring your next concert! So no
complaining!
55:
Huh, he's not lying. This has text and
art for the local burger joint.
60:
...W-well, if it's for my next
performance, I guess I've gotta do
whatever I can.
65: That's the spirit! Now get to work.
71:
Wait, you want me to hand these
out right NOW? A little warning
beforehand would've been nice!
76:
You want to repay our generous
sponsor by being lazy? No? Then
you better work up a sweat and
pass these out!
82: When you put it that way...
87:
I look forward to handing these
tissues out.
92:
Come for food and music at Burger
Karatsu! Our special concert is
starting soon!
93:
You won't want to miss the tasty
burgers at Burger Karatsu!
97:
You'd think more people would want
free tissues, but we're not getting
many takers...
102:
Maybe there's a more efficient way
than handing out each packet one
by one.
107:
That's probably true, but the goal
here isn't to empty our stock as fast
as possible.
109:
How do I put it... We need the people
to remember our faces too.
113:
That's why you've gotta go at it with
all you've got! Put some heart into
your efforts, you know?
125:
Come see us at Burger Karatsu for
tasty food and awesome music!
Oh! Thank you very much!
129:
That's almost all our tissues. You
made the right call, Sakura.
134:
This girl here is Number 2, and this
one here is Number 3.
139:
That... is not what I meant when 
I said they needed to "remember 
our faces"...
146:
If it isn't Number 1! 
You sure put on a show the other day.
150:
That is NOT a face I wanted to see
again! What do we do?!
154:
Some people just dunno when to
give up! Let's get outta here!
157:
You actually think I'm gonna let you
go?
173: Eeeeek! I didn't sign up for THIS!
175: Uh, hey... Why can't I move?
177:
Your head popped off when you fell
over! We gotta get you fixed up
before anyone else sees—
183:
Shoot, too late for that! Think fast,
guys—
190:
Everyone, please pay attention.
Sakura, this is your cue.
194:
Huh?! Uh... Well... Please come visit
us at Burger Karatsu! We've got
great food and music waiting!
195:
I'm an idol from the group
Franchouchou! We're so passionate
about our music, we "lose our
heads" over it! Haha! Ha!
198:
We hope you enjoyed the illusion
show.
201: Ohhh, it was all a performance...
202:
Totally fooled me. That burger place
really upped their ad game.
206: I can't believe they bought it...
211:
Phew! You're a lifesaver, Stella. 
I totally thought my secret was out...
215:
They will remember us now, won't
they?
219:
I don't think they could forget us,
even if they wanted to! It was super
effective!
221: Let's keep up the good work!
